    </ShowcaseHeader>
    <ShowcaseSection>
      <template #title>Intro</template>
      <template #content>
        <ShowcaseParagraph>
          When I lived in Uruguay, I worked together with Nativeway, a startup that teaches young
          and old the English language.
          <br />
          Their classes are taught from a native point of view, something that you don’t see much in
          South America. Their educational material reflects real-world interactions as much as
          possible. In this way, the student learns more naturally and less forced English.
        </ShowcaseParagraph>
      </template>
    </ShowcaseSection>
    <ShowcaseSection>
      <template #title>Seriously fun</template>
      <template #content>
        <ShowcaseParagraph>
          Learning English is fun, and everyone can do it. To reflect this ideology, the colors
          purple and orange were picked. The design integrates playful illustrations to make the
          content stand out in a friendly way.
        </ShowcaseParagraph>
        <div class="flex">
          <ShowcaseImage>
            <NuxtPicture
              preset="image"
              src="images/showcase/nativeway/homepage.png"
              :srcset="getImageSrcSet('images/showcase/nativeway/homepage.png', [{ width: 900 }])"
              class="w-full"
            />
          </ShowcaseImage>
        </div>
      </template>
    </ShowcaseSection>
    <ShowcaseSection>
      <template #title>General english test</template>
      <template #content>
        <ShowcaseParagraph>
          To help you find the right course, we need to determine your current English knowledge. I
          created a short questionnaire test to help you determine this. Try it out here.
        </ShowcaseParagraph>
        <ShowcaseImage class="w-full">
          <NuxtPicture
            preset="image"
            src="images/showcase/nativeway/english-test.png"
            :srcset="getImageSrcSet('images/showcase/nativeway/english-test.png', [{ width: 900 }])"
            class="w-full"
          />
        </ShowcaseImage>
      </template>
    </ShowcaseSection>
    <ShowcaseSection>
      <template #title>Development</template>
